  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this open-label, single-arm, multicenter, post-marketing trial is to evaluate
      long-term safety of Firmagon® in approximately 230 Indian patients diagnosed with advanced
      hormone-dependent prostate cancer requiring androgen deprivation therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
